SERVICE CLOUD
Call Center Fields

All call centers include these required fields:

REQUIRED EDITIONS
Available in: Salesforce Classic and Lightning Experience
Available in: Essentials, Professional, Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer Editions

FIELD	DESCRIPTION
Internal Name	Represents the unique identifier for the call center.
Display Name	Represents the name of the call center as displayed in Salesforce.
Description	Represents a description of the call center.

SEE ALSO
Display and Edit a Call Center
Create a Call Center
Manage Call Center Users
